dct_description_sm: Title from panel. Relief on Uruguay map is shown by gradient tints and spot heights. "© ITMB Publishing 2015". Includes indexes, location map, and color illustrations. Incudes ancillary maps on recto: Colonia del Sacramento, city centre inset --Punta del Este, city centre. On verso: Montevideo, regional inset.
